expression: stdout
---
Build a Pit House coexistence receipt from observed case artifact files

Usage: wheelctl moza pit-house-proof [OPTIONS] --lane <LANE> --closed-artifact <CLOSED_ARTIFACT> --open-standard-artifact <OPEN_STANDARD_ARTIFACT> --direct-artifact <DIRECT_ARTIFACT> --mode-change-artifact <MODE_CHANGE_ARTIFACT> --firmware-page-artifact <FIRMWARE_PAGE_ARTIFACT>

Options:
      --json
          Output in JSON format for machine parsing
      --lane <LANE>
          Lane artifact directory, e.g. ci/hardware/moza-r5/2026-05-06
      --closed-artifact <CLOSED_ARTIFACT>
          Artifact for Pit House closed case
  -v, --verbose...
          Verbose logging
      --open-standard-artifact <OPEN_STANDARD_ARTIFACT>
          Artifact for Pit House open, idle, standard-mode case
      --direct-artifact <DIRECT_ARTIFACT>
          Artifact for Pit House open, direct-mode case
      --mode-change-artifact <MODE_CHANGE_ARTIFACT>
          Artifact for Pit House mode-change-during-run case
      --firmware-page-artifact <FIRMWARE_PAGE_ARTIFACT>
          Artifact for Pit House firmware/update page case
      --shared-control-risk <SHARED_CONTROL_RISK>
          Shared-control risk outcome: detected, warned, or documented_limit [default: warned]
      --json-out <JSON_OUT>
          Write the Pit House proof receipt to this JSON file
      --overwrite
          Replace an existing proof receipt
  -h, --help
          Print help
